reviewText:
I have played and loved the EBF series for a long time, so this may be baised, but I don't care. But first, let me ask you something;
In what other game do you get to destroy monsters, no-  ecosystems  by using nukes, blackholes, or perhaps making it rain giant fiery swords? Because I can't think of one. If that isn't enough reason to like it, I don't know what you're looking for. But, I can bet you that you can find it in EBF4.

Hail Newgrounds. Wait, no. Hail Matt Roszak.
